## Scenario

A small organization needs visibility into endpoint activity and security events. A SOC analyst deploys Wazuh to monitor endpoint logs, review alerts, identify suspicious activity, and document recommended remediation steps.

This lab simulates that workflow by setting up Wazuh, onboarding endpoints, validating alert visibility, and documenting how an analyst would investigate and respond to security events.

