## Lessons Learned

This lab helped me understand that deploying a SIEM is only the first step. The real value comes from reviewing alerts, understanding event context, identifying risk, reducing false positives, and documenting response actions clearly.

It also reinforced the importance of endpoint visibility, structured investigation, and practical reporting in SOC operations.

